Governor of Oyo State, ‘Seyi Makinde will on Friday, June 3rd, meet all aspirants who procured expression of Interest and nomination forms, and those who emerged as candidates of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP). This was contained in a notice issued by the State Secretary of the party, Alhaji Wasiu Adeleke. It reads: “This is to inform all House of Assembly, House of Representatives and Senatorial Aspirants and Candidates of our party that there will be a meeting with the Executive Governor of Oyo State, Governor ‘Seyi Makinde on Friday, 3rd of June 2022 at the Government House, Agodi, Ibadan by 10am prompt.” -Advertisement- According to a news platform, Goalpoachernews, Makinde may use the avenue to formally present his running mate to all the party executives and stakeholders who would be attending the meeting.